oEEt6uv_sgZk07Q">Nhàn vịnh kỳ 08 - 間詠其八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Nh%E1%BA%ADp-H%C3%A0nh-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-RaTSZaUHzh49rWc6QXWeqw">Nhập Hành Châu - 入衡州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-%C4%91%C3%A3i-Nghi%C3%AAm-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-phu/poem-5RxB5pwFct9hnenhIGkKwQ">Phụng đãi Nghiêm đại phu - 奉待嚴大夫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Qu%C3%BD-T%E1%BB%B5-thu-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-th%C4%83ng-S%C6%A1n-Nam-x%E1%BB%A9-T%E1%BA%A3-m%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%91%C4%83ng-tr%C3%ACnh-ng%E1%BA%ABu-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc/poem-5YnPZj1DPRNHxnrISZqDWg">Quý Tỵ thu phụng thăng Sơn Nam xứ Tả mạc đăng trình ngẫu đắc - 癸巳秋奉陞山南處左瘼登程偶得</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Ngao/poem-w_OMVHVuiVnLMUqZGoDfZg">Thượng Ngao - 上嶅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
